import React, { useContext } from 'react' import dateFormat from 'dateformat' import './Card.css' import { Context } from '../../Store/AppContext'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; const Card = (props) => { const {country, city, monday, monday_img, monday_max, monday_min,tuesday, tuesday_max, tuesday_min,wednesday, wednesday_max, wednesday_min,thursday, thursday_max, thursday_min, friday_max , friday_min, saturday_max, saturday_min, sunday_max, sunday_min,tuesday_img, wednesday_img, thursday_img ,friday_img, saturday_img, sunday_img} = props return (

{city}

{country}

{dateFormat(monday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{monday_max}°/{monday_min}°

{dateFormat(tuesday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{tuesday_max}°/{tuesday_min}°

{dateFormat(wednesday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{wednesday_max}°/{wednesday_min}°

{dateFormat(thursday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{thursday_max}°/{thursday_min}°

{dateFormat(friday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{friday_max}°/{friday_min}°

{dateFormat(monday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{monday_max}°/{monday_min}°

{dateFormat(monday,"dddd, mmmm d, yyyy")}

{monday_max}°/{monday_min}°

) } export default Card
